  <brief_title>Everyday Practice With Transcatheter Aortic Valve Implantation</brief_title>
  <acronym>EVERY-TAVI</acronym>
  <official_title>Experience With Percutaneous Transcatheter Aortic Valve Implantation in Patients With Symptomatic Aortic Valve Disease in Two German Centers</official_title>
  <sponsors>
